  "description": "A long exposure night shot of a bridge illuminated with vibrant colors reflecting on the water below. The bridge is a suspension type, appearing large and spanning a wide body of water. The lights on the bridge are a mix of white, red, and blue, creating a festive and dynamic visual. The water surface is rippled and sparkly due to the reflections of the lights and perhaps slight waves. A shoreline with dim lights is visible in the distance, and the sky is a deep, dark blue, almost black. The foreground includes a dark, blurred edge suggesting a viewing point like a pier or embankment.",
